Title Return the list of documents for a series-jurisdiction combination

get_documents.Rd

Title Return the list of documents for a series-jurisdiction combination

get_documents(jurisdiction, document_type = 3)

Arguments

jurisdiction

Integer - ID of jurisdiction of interest
document_type

Integer - ID of document type of interest. Obtain from get_document_types().

Value

data frame

Examples

get_documents(38,3)
